    <p>MARIAH CAREY’S MAG­I­CAL CHRIST­MAS SPE­CIAL 43 min­utes/Ap­ple TV+</p>
    <p>Of course Mariah Carey has a Christ­mas TV mu­si­cal spe­cial – her iconic an­them All I Want For Christ­mas Is You is the best-sell­ing hol­i­day sin­gle of all time.</p>
    <p>There is a plot too – Santa Claus turns to his good friend Mariah to solve a global fes­tive cheer cri­sis.</p>
    <p>There are guest stars aplenty, such as mil­len­nial pop star Ari­ana Grande, come­di­enne Tif­fany Had­dish, hip-hop vet­eran Snoop Dogg and even car­toon icon Snoopy.</p>
    <p>If you can­not get enough of the songs, Mariah Carey’s Mag­i­cal Christ­mas Spe­cial (Ap­ple TV+ Orig­i­nal Sound­track) is avail­able on mu­sic stream­ing ser­vices such as Ap­ple Mu­sic and Spo­tify.</p>

